quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,"By the fig and the olive"
  95,2,"and the Mount Sinai"
  95,3,"and this land secure!"
  95,4,"We indeed created Man in the fairest stature"
  95,5,"then We restored him the lowest of the low --"
  95,6,"save those who believe, and do righteous deeds; they shall have a wage unfailing."
  95,7,"What then shall cry thee lies as to the Doom?"
  95,8,"Is not God the justest of judges?"
